### Upload EPUB — 201 Created
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=PlumBoundary

--PlumBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="pride.epub"
Content-Type: application/epub+zip

< /tmp/epubs/pride.epub
--PlumBoundary--

> {%
client.global.set("bookId", response.body.book.id);
%}

###

### Upload same EPUB again → 201 with deduplicated: true
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=PlumBoundary

--PlumBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="pride.epub"
Content-Type: application/epub+zip

< /tmp/epubs/pride.epub
--PlumBoundary--

###

### Upload wrong file → 422 invalid_epub
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=PlumBoundary

--PlumBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="garbage.epub"
Content-Type: application/epub+zip

not actually an epub
--PlumBoundary--

###

### Upload .pdf → 422 unsupported_file
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=PlumBoundary

--PlumBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="x.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

%PDF-1.4
--PlumBoundary--
